Package request

Class Request

  • java.lang.Object
    • request.Request
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Request
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a Request object. Request objects have a string content, username of the requester, and an int requestStatus that contains the status of the request.
